data.description: First Time on the Market! This home offers 3 bedrooms on the main level with either a non-conforming bedroom or use as an office and has 2 and a half Bathrooms. In the lower level, lots of storage or game area, plus there is a finished room that could be used as a bedroom or an office with a full bath attached to it. Also, with a walk up attic, there is lots of storage room or possibly add bonus rooms. This Property sits on 5 acres with a 3 stall horse barn and a round training pen. So if your looking for a small farmette or your own slice of the county, Schedule your appointment today!
